graph TB
    Dev([Developer Edits Prompt]) --> Git[Git Commit + PR]
    
    Git --> Review[Peer Review<br/>Human checks prompt changes]
    
    Review -->|Approved| CI[CI Pipeline Triggers]
    Review -->|Rejected| Dev
    
    subgraph CI [Automated Test Suite]
        Golden[Golden Dataset<br/>200+ test cases] --> Run[Run All Tests<br/>temp=0 for determinism]
        Run --> Assert[Assertions:<br/>contains / not-contains /<br/>BERTScore / LLM-judge]
    end
    
    Assert --> Gate{Quality Gate}
    
    Gate -->|Faithfulness < 90%| BLOCK[DEPLOY BLOCKED<br/>Fix before proceeding]
    Gate -->|Accuracy dropped > 2%| BLOCK
    Gate -->|All pass| Canary
    
    BLOCK --> Dev
    
    subgraph Canary [Canary Deploy]
        C10[10% traffic → new version<br/>90% → current version]
        C10 --> Monitor24[Monitor 24 hours]
    end
    
    Monitor24 --> CanaryGate{Canary Check}
    
    CanaryGate -->|Metrics healthy| Rollout50[50% traffic]
    CanaryGate -->|Degradation| Rollback[Instant Rollback<br/>revert git commit]
    
    Rollout50 --> Full[100% traffic<br/>New version is now production]
    Rollback --> Dev
    
    Full --> OngoingMonitor
    
    subgraph OngoingMonitor [Production Monitoring]
        Dashboard[Dashboard:<br/>latency p50/p95/p99<br/>error rate<br/>cost vs budget]
        Weekly[Weekly: sample 1% traffic<br/>LLM-as-judge quality score]
        Nightly[Nightly: re-run golden tests<br/>catch provider model updates]
    end
    
    OngoingMonitor -->|Issue detected| Alert[Alert → Dev]
    Alert --> Dev
    
    subgraph Version Registry
        V1[prompt-v1 — archived]
        V2[prompt-v2 — production]
        V3[prompt-v3 — staging]
    end

    style Git fill:#8957e5,color:#fff
    style Gate fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style BLOCK fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style Canary fill:#d29922,color:#000
    style Full fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style Rollback fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style Dashboard fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff
